<span data-ttu-id="29605-1494">Izvještava o radnji koja čita označeni unos iz ugrađenog potpisa exe datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1494">Reports on the action that reads tagged input from the exe's embedded signature.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="29605-1495">Ovo je nedokazani koncept koji prethodna iteracija izvršne datoteke setup.exe nije implementirala i na što se oslanjamo u prenošenju korisnikovih izbora proizvoda/jezika/broja bitova s web-stranice na proces unutar izvršne datoteke setup.exe.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1495">This is an unproven concept the previous iteration of setup.exe did not implement, and is what we're relying on to carry the user's product/language/bitness choices from web page to in-process within setup.exe.</span></span>

### <a name="officeserviceabilitymanagerinventoryaddonheartbeat"></a><span data-ttu-id="29605-1555">Office.ServiceabilityManager.InventoryAddon.Heartbeat</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1555">Office.ServiceabilityManager.InventoryAddon.Heartbeat</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="29605-1556">*[Ovaj je događaj uklonjen iz trenutačnih međuverzija sustava Office, ali se i dalje može pojavljivati u starijim međuverzijama.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1556">*[This event has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="29605-1557">Taj se događaj koristi za pribavljanje standardnih meta-podataka pri svakom pokretanju dodatka Inventar, koji je dio Upravitelja za Office servisiranje i koristi se za informacije o Office inventaru na onim strojevima koje je IT administrator uključio.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1557">This event is used to acquire standard metadata on each run of the Inventory add-on, which is part of the Office Serviceability Manager and is used for inventory Office information on those machines for which an IT admin has opted in.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="29605-1558">Meta-podatak od posebnog zanimanja u ovom slučaju je ID sesije, a koristi se za povezivanje s drugim podacima pohranjenima unutar usluge na oblaku po klijentu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1558">The metadata of specific interest here is the session ID, and it is used for linking to other data stored within a per-tenant cloud service.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="29605-1559">Ovaj događaj nema dodatnih polja jer su relevantni samo meta-podaci.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1559">This event contains no extra fields since only the metadata is relevant.</span></span>

### <a name="officeserviceabilitymanagerinventoryaddonresults"></a><span data-ttu-id="29605-1560">Office.ServiceabilityManager.InventoryAddon.Results</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1560">Office.ServiceabilityManager.InventoryAddon.Results</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="29605-1561">Taj se događaj bilježi kada se poziv na web-servis u sklopu dodatka "klikom do cilja" za inventar upravitelja za servis dovrši, neovisno o tome uspijeva li ili ne uspijeva.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1561">This event is logged when the call to the webservice made within the Click-to-Run Serviceability Manager Inventory add-on completes, irrespective of whether it succeeds or fails.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="29605-1562">To je u suštini posljednja operacija unutar dodatka za praćenje ukupnog stanja rada.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1562">This is essentially the last operation within the add-on to track the overall operation status.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="29605-1563">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1563">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1564">**ActionDetail** – dodatne pojedinosti u slučaju nastupanja kvara.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1564">**ActionDetail** -  Additional details for when a failure occurs.</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1565">Ako zahtjev HTTP-a uspije, ActionDetail bit će 0.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1565">If the HTTP request succeeds, ActionDetail will be 0.</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1566">Ako Polje rezultata nije U redu (tj. nije 0), što znači da zahtjev nije poslan, u ovom će se polju zabilježiti kod interne pogreške koji je jednak Polju rezultata.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1566">If the Result field is not OK (i.e. not 0), which means that the request is not sent, this field will log the internal error code which is the same as the Result field.</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1567">Ako je Polje rezultata U redu (tj. 0), što znači da je kôd odgovora HTTP-a >= 300, u njemu će se zabilježiti kôd odgovora HTTP-a (npr. 404).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1567">If the Result field is OK (i.e. 0), which means that the HTTP response code >= 300, it will log the HTTP response code (e.g. 404).</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1568">**Rezultat** – brojčana oznaka pogreške koju vraćaju API-jevi poziva web-servisa sustava Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1568">**Result** - Numeric error code flags returned by the Office webservice call APIs.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="29605-1569">– npr. 3 znači da postoji problem s inicijalizacijom zaglavlja HTTP-a.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1569">– e.g. 3 would mean that there was a problem initializing the HTTP headers.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1570">**Type** – dodatne informacije o vrsti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1570">**Type** - Additional type information.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="29605-1571">U slučaju Zaliha, ove informacije određuju vrstu tereta koji se šalje – npr. pune ili samo delta promjene.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1571">In the case of the Inventory, this information specifies the type of payload being sent – e.g. full or just a delta of changes.</span></span> 

-  <span data-ttu-id="29605-1572">**WebCallSource** – vrijednost za numeriranje (koja se određuje kao cijeli broj) koja označava dodatak upravitelja servisa koji je bio izvor poziva:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1572">**WebCallSource** - An enumeration value (specified as an integer) indicating the Serviceability Manager add-on that was the source of the call:</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1573">Zalihe: 0</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1573">Inventory: 0</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1574">Konfiguriranje zaliha: 1</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1574">Inventory Configuration: 1</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1575">Pravilnik o zalihama: 2</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1575">Inventory Policy: 2</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1576">Stanje mreže zaliha: 3</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1576">Inventory Network Status: 3</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1577">Upravitelj servisa: 4</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1577">Serviceability Manager: 4</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1578">Mogućnost upravljanja: 5</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1578">Manageability: 5</span></span>

### <a name="officeserviceabilitymanagerwebservicefailure"></a><span data-ttu-id="29605-1579">Office.ServiceabilityManager.WebserviceFailure</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1579">Office.ServiceabilityManager.WebserviceFailure</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="29605-1580">Ova se naredba bilježi svaki put kad ne uspije poziv na web-servis unutar jednog od dodataka upravitelja servisa sustava Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1580">Whenever a call to a webservice within one of the Office Serviceability Manager add-ins fails, this statement is logged.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="29605-1581">Pogreške mogu nastati zbog unutarnjih pogrešaka ili nemogućnosti povezivanja s web-servisom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1581">Failures can be due to internal failures or an inability to connect to the webservice.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="29605-1582">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1582">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1583">**Add-on** - Programski dodatak upravitelja servisa "klikom do cilja" iz kojeg je pokrenut poziv na web-servis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1583">**Add-on** - The Click-to-Run Serviceability Manager add-on from which the webservice call was made.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="29605-1584">To može imati vrijednosti kao što su zalihe, upravljanje itd., kodirane kao numerička vrijednost.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1584">This can have values like inventory, manageability, etc. encoded as a numeric value.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1585">**Correlation ID** – nasumično generirani GUID specifičan za trenutnu instancu koji je poslan web-servisu kako bi povezao pozive između klijenta i poslužitelja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1585">**Correlation ID** - A randomly generated GUID specific to the current instance that is sent to the webservice to correlate calls between the client and the server.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1586">**ErrorInfo** - brojčana oznaka pogreške koju vraćaju API-jevi poziva web-servisa sustava Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1586">**ErrorInfo** - Numeric error code information returned by the Office webservice call APIs.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1587">**ErrorMessage** – poruka koja omogućuje daljnji uvid u pogrešku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1587">**ErrorMessage** - A message providing further insight into the failure.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="29605-1588">Svaka se vrsta greške mapira na niz ugrađen u kôd, a neke se vrste grešaka mapiraju na potencijalno više nizova ovisno o posebnoj vrsti greške.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1588">Each error type maps to a hardcoded string, with some error types mapping to potentially multiple strings depending on the specific nature of the failure.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1589">**Function** – funkcija u kodu iz koje je došlo do trenutnog poziva.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1589">**Function** - The function in the code from which the current call occurred.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1590">**Status** – kôd HTTP-a kojeg vraća poziv web-servisu, npr. 404, 500, itd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1590">**Status** - The HTTP status code returned by the call to the webservice, e.g. 404, 500, etc.</span></span>

### <a name="officeexperimentationtriggeranalysis"></a><span data-ttu-id="29605-1606">Office. Experimentation. TriggerAnalysis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1606">Office.Experimentation.TriggerAnalysis</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="29605-1607">Ovaj događaj pomaže analizi opsega upotrebe proizvoda i parametara performansi (poput rušenja, prekida i sl.) podskupini korisnika ili uređaja koji ispunjavaju uvjete za upotrebu ove značajke i na taj način pomažu u osiguravanju ispravnog rada proizvoda.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1607">This event helps scope analysis of product usage and performance metrics (such as crashes, hangs, etc.) to the subset of users or devices that are eligible to use the feature, thereby helping ensure that the product is working properly.</span></span>

### <a name="onenoteflightdefault"></a><span data-ttu-id="29605-1610">OneNote.FlightDefault</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1610">OneNote.FlightDefault</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="29605-1611">Taj se događaj bilježi kada OneNote zatraži od poslužitelja ECS vrijednosti letenja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1611">This event is logged when OneNote asks ECS server for flight values.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="29605-1612">To se koristi da bi se omogućile eksperimentalne značajke korisnicima koji su se uključili u primanje ovakvih letova.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1612">This is used to enable experimental features to those users who have opted in for receiving such flights.</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="29605-1613">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1613">The following fields are collected:</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1614">**ConfigParam** – konfiguracija za koju se pristupa vrijednostima za</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1614">**ConfigParam** - The config for which the value is being accessed for</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingaccepteulaforcurrentlicense"></a><span data-ttu-id="29605-1616">Office.Licensing.AcceptEulaForCurrentLicense</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1616">Office.Licensing.AcceptEulaForCurrentLicense</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="29605-1617">To se prikuplja kad korisnik dobije licencu i prihvati EULA-u za trenutnu licencu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1617">This is collected when the user gets licensed and accepts EULA for the current license</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="29605-1618">Koristi se radi otkrivanja je li korisnik u dobrom stanju, koristi se u svrhe određivanja stanja sustava i za dijagnostiku ako korisnik prijavi problem s računalom</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1618">It is used to detect if the user is in a good state or not, used for system health and used for diagnostic purposes if a user reports an issue with their machine</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingactivation"></a><span data-ttu-id="29605-1622">Office.Licensing.Activation</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1622">Office.Licensing.Activation</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="29605-1623">Nakon postavljanja licence na računalu pokušavamo licencu aktivirati pozivanjem servisa AVS.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1623">Post setting up the license on the machine, we attempt to activate the license by calling the AVS service.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="29605-1624">Ovo prijavljuje rezultat poziva radi aktivacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1624">This reports the result of the activation call</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="29605-1625">Ključno je za otkrivanje koliko bi korisnika moglo imati problema s aktivacijom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1625">It is critical in detecting how many users are facing activation issues.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="29605-1626">Za otkrivanje eventualnih regresija imamo otkrivanje anomalija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1626">We have anomaly detection to detect any regression.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="29605-1627">To je izuzetno važno jer ovisimo o vanjskom servisu AVS, pa nam ovaj signal pokazuje je li stanje naših vanjskih partnera dobro.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1627">This is super critical as we have an external dependency on AVS and this signal points whether our external partners are healthy .</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="29605-1628">Koristi se i u dijagnostičke svrhe te za utvrđivanje stanja sustava ako korisnik priajvi problem s uređajem</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1628">It is also used for diagnostic purposes and system health if a user reports an issue with their machine</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="29605-1629">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1629">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1630">**Acid** – GUID identifikator koji predstavlja proizvod sustava Office za koji korisnik ima licencu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1630">**Acid** - A GUID identifier representing the Office product that the user is licensed for</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1631">**ReferralData** – identifikator OEM-a koji je instalirao Office na računalo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1631">**ReferralData** – Identifier of the OEM that installed Office on the machine</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingactivationwizard"></a><span data-ttu-id="29605-1632">Office.Licensing.ActivationWizard</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1632">Office.Licensing.ActivationWizard</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="29605-1633">Ako zbog nekog razloga ne možemo automatski aktivirati licencu, korisniku prikazujemo čarobnjak za aktivaciju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1633">If we are not able to automatically activate the license for some reason, we show an activation wizard to the user.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="29605-1634">Ovo prijavljuje da je korisniku prikazan čarobnjak.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1634">This reports that the wizard is being shown to the user.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="29605-1635">Ključno je radi otkrivanja je li korisnik u dobrom stanju te da mu ne nedostaje neka funkcija, koristi se u svrhe određivanja stanja sustava i za dijagnostiku ako korisnik prijavi problem s računalom</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1635">It is critical in detecting if the user is in a good state and not missing functionality, used for system health and used for diagnostic purposes if a user reports an issue with their machine</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="29605-1636">Događaj ne prikuplja nijedno polje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1636">This event collects no fields.</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingenforcesigninqualified"></a><span data-ttu-id="29605-1637">Office.Licensing.EnforceSignInQualified</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1637">Office.Licensing.EnforceSignInQualified</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="29605-1638">Taj nam signal daje do znanja je li eksperiment koji smo pokrenuli radi prisilne prijave korisnika u sklopu licenciranja uspio.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1638">This is the signal that tells us if the experiment that we are running to enforce user sign as part of licensing is successful.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="29605-1639">Ključan je za otkrivanje uspješnosti ili pogreške eksperimenta kojim se korisnika prisiljava na prijavu, a to je obavezan korak modernog stoga za licenciranje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1639">This is critical in detecting the success or failure of the experiment that is forcing the users to login which is a required step for the modern licensing stack.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="29605-1640">Ako se korisnik ne prijavi, neće moći koristiti aplikaciju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1640">Failure to sign in will result in the users not being able to use the app.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="29605-1641">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1641">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1642">**Qualified** – određuje je li korisnik kvalificiran za prisilnu prijavu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1642">**Qualified** – Identifies whether the user qualified for the sign in enforcement</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingexpirationdialogshown"></a><span data-ttu-id="29605-1643">Office.Licensing.ExpirationDialogShown</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1643">Office.Licensing.ExpirationDialogShown</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="29605-1644">To se prikuplja kad korisniku prikažemo dijaloški okvir o isteku koji ga obavještava da je licenca istekla. Ključno je radi otkrivanja je li korisnik u dobrom stanju te da mu ne nedostaje neka funkcija, koristi se u svrhe određivanja stanja sustava i za dijagnostiku ako korisnik prijavi problem s računalom</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1644">This is collected when we show the expiration dialog to the user that says that their license has expired It is critical in detecting if the user is in a good state and not missing functionality, used for system health and used for diagnostic purposes if a user reports an issue with their machine</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="29605-1645">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1645">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1646">**LicNotificationState** – identifikator koji nas obavještava o tome kakve se obavijesti prikazuju korisniku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1646">**LicNotificationState** – An enumerator that tells us what kind of notification is being shown to the user</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingfullvalidation"></a><span data-ttu-id="29605-1647">Office.Licensing.FullValidation</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1647">Office.Licensing.FullValidation</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="29605-1648">To se prikupljaju u svakoj sesiji koja prijavljuje stanje licenciranja računala te prijavljuje pogreške koje se korisniku prikazuju i zbog kojih ne može koristiti aplikaciju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1648">This is collected on every session that reports the licensing state of the machine and reports the errors that the user is seeing due to which they are not able to use the application.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="29605-1649">Događaj označava je li korisnikovo računalo u dobrom stanju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1649">This event indicates if the user's machine is healthy or not.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="29605-1650">Za taj smo događaj postavili otkrivanje anomalija da bismo prepoznali uzrokuje li regresija ili mehanizam aktivacije negativno ponašanje korisnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1650">We have anomaly detection set up for this event to indicate if a regression or activation mechanism is causing bad user behavior.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="29605-1651">Ključno je i za dijagnosticiranje korisničkih problema te za praćenje stanja sustava.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1651">This is also critical when diagnosing user issues and for monitoring system health.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="29605-1652">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1652">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1653">**Acid** – GUID identifikator koji predstavlja proizvod sustava Office za koji korisnik ima licencu </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1653">**Acid** – A GUID identifier representing the Office product that the user is licensed for</span></span> 
  
  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1654">**Atributi Activationatribute**-vrsta mehanizma aktivacije koji korisnik upotrebljava.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1654">**ActivationAttributes** - Type of activation mechanism that the user is using.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1655">**IsSessionLicensing** – određuje je li trenutno pokrenut način rada za aktivaciju zajedničkog računala</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1655">**IsSessionLicensing** – Whether we are currently running under shared computer activation mode or not</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1656">**LicenseCategory** – kategorija licence za Office koju korisnik koristi </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1656">**LicenseCategory** – Category of the Office license that the user is using</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1657">**Licenses** – popis naziva svih licenci za Office koje postoje na računalu </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1657">**Licenses** – List of names of all the  Office licenses that are present on the machine</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1658">**LicenseStatuses** – status svih licenci za Office koje postoje na računalu </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1658">**LicenseStatuses** – Status of all the Office licenses present on the machine</span></span> 

### <a name="officelicensinggetentitlement"></a><span data-ttu-id="29605-1659">Office.Licensing.GetEntitlement</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1659">Office.Licensing.GetEntitlement</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="29605-1660">To prikupljamo kad korisnik postavlja uređaj te pozivamo servis za licenciranje da otkrije ima li prijavljeni korisnik prava na Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1660">We collect this when the user is setting up a device and we call our licensing service to detect if the logged in user has an Office entitlement or not.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="29605-1661">Prijavljuje rezultat poziva</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1661">This reports the result of that call.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="29605-1662">Ključno je radi otkrivanja je li korisnik u dobrom stanju te da mu ne nedostaje neka funkcija, koristi se u svrhe određivanja stanja sustava i za dijagnostiku ako korisnik prijavi problem s računalom</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1662">It is critical in detecting if the user is in a good state and missing functionality, used for system health and used for diagnostic purposes if a user reports an issue with their machine</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="29605-1663">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1663">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1664">**EntitlementCount** – Broj prava koja korisnik ima</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1664">**EntitlementCount** – Number of entitlements the user has</span></span>


### <a name="officelicensingheartbeat"></a><span data-ttu-id="29605-1665">Office.Licensing.Heartbeat</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1665">Office.Licensing.Heartbeat</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="29605-1666">Za svaku sesiju provjeravamo je li prošlo 72 sata od zadnje obnove licence te pokušavamo produljiti vrijeme do isteka trenutne licence.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1666">On every session we check if 72 hours have passed since the last license renewal and try to extend the expiry of the current license.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="29605-1667">Događaj prijavljuje uspješnost ili pogrešku poziva koji upućujemo radi provjere možemo li produljiti vrijeme do isteka licence i zadržati funkcionalnost korisnikove instalacije sustava Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1667">This event reports the success or failure of the call that we make to ensure we can extend the expiry of the license and keep the user's Office installation functional.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="29605-1668">Ključan je za dijagnosticiranje problema povezanih s pretplatom i problema sa servisom za korisnika te za otkrivanje regresija već aktiviranih korisnika pretplate.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1668">It is critical in diagnosing subscription related issues and service issues for the user and is critical in detecting regressions for already activated subscription users.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="29605-1669">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1669">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1670">**Mode** – prikaz stoga licenciranja sustava Office koji se koristi na ovom računalu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1670">**Mode** – An enumerator representation of the Office licensing stack that is being used on this machine</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensinginclientpinredemptioncallpinredemptionapi"></a><span data-ttu-id="29605-1671">Office.Licensing.InClientPinRedemption.CallPinRedemptionAPI</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1671">Office.Licensing.InClientPinRedemption.CallPinRedemptionAPI</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="29605-1672">Ta telemetrija prati rezultate otkupnog poziva servisa PIN sustava Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1672">This telemetry tracks the results of Office's pin redemption service call.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="29605-1673">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1673">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1674">**ClientTransactionId**- jedinstveni identifikator za poziv servisa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1674">**ClientTransactionId** - Unique identifier for the service call.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1675">**ErrorCategory** – svaka vrsta pogreške može se nalaziti u više općenitim kategorijama, npr. „Retryable”.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1675">**ErrorCategory** - Each error type can fall into a more general category, such as "Retryable".</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1676">**ErrorType** – razlog neuspjeha, kao što je „AlreadyRedeemedByOther”.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1676">**ErrorType** - Reason of failure, such as "AlreadyRedeemedByOther".</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1677">**InAFOFlow** – Booleova oznaka koja upućuje na to da je u tijeku AFO iskupljenje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1677">**InAFOFlow** - A Boolean indicating if we are in the AFO redemption flow.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1678">**StatusCode** – rezultat servisnog poziva od jedne riječi, poput „Created”.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1678">**StatusCode** - One-word result of the service call, such as "Created".</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1679">**StatusMessage** – pojedinosti o kôdu statusa, kao što je „Uspješno dodijeljeno”.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1679">**StatusMessage** - Details of the status code, such as 'Successfully provisioned."</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1680">**UsingNulApi**- Booleova vrijednost koja upućuje na to da li koristimo novi stog licenci za licenciranje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1680">**UsingNulApi** - A Boolean indicating if we are using the new licensing stack.</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensinginrfm"></a><span data-ttu-id="29605-1681">Office.Licensing.InRFM</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1681">Office.Licensing.InRFM</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="29605-1682">Ako uređaj prijeđe u način rada smanjene funkcionalnosti, šaljemo signal koji označava da računalo nije u dobrom stanju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1682">If the device enters reduced functionality mode, we send out this signal to indicate that the machine is not in a healthy state.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="29605-1683">Ključno je radi otkrivanja je li korisnik u dobrom stanju te da mu ne nedostaje neka funkcija, koristi se u svrhe određivanja stanja sustava i za dijagnostiku ako korisnik prijavi problem s računalom</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1683">It is critical in detecting if the user is in a good state and missing functionality, used for system health and used for diagnostic purposes if a user reports an issue with their machine</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1685">**ACID** – GUID identifikator koji predstavlja proizvod sustava Office za koji korisnik ima licencu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1685">**ACID** - A GUID identifier representing the Office product that the user is licensed for</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1686">**DaysRemaining** – broj dana do isteka trenutne licence za Office</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1686">**DaysRemaining** - Number of days remaining before the current Office license expires</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1687">**Mode** – prikaz stoga licenciranja sustava Office koji se koristi na računalu kao identifikatora</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1687">**Mode** – An enumerator representation of the Office licensing stack that is being used on this machine</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1688">**ProductName** – naziv proizvoda koji korisnik trenutno upotrebljava</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1688">**ProductName** – Name of the product that the user is currently using</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1689">**Reason** – šifra pogreške koja označava razlog trenutnog statusa licence</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1689">**Reason** – The error code indicating the reason for the current status of the license</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensinginstallkey"></a><span data-ttu-id="29605-1690">Office.Licensing.InstallKey</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1690">Office.Licensing.InstallKey</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="29605-1691">To se prikuplja kad pokušamo instalirati ključ na uređaj radi licenciranja računala.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1691">This is collected when we try to install a key on the device to license the machine.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="29605-1692">Prijavljuje je li instalacija uspjela, a ako nije, prijavljuje šifru pogreške.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1692">It reports whether the installation was successful and if it was not then the error code.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="29605-1693">Ključno je radi otkrivanja je li korisnik u dobrom stanju te da mu ne nedostaje neka funkcija, koristi se u svrhe određivanja stanja sustava i za dijagnostiku ako korisnik prijavi problem s računalom</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1693">It is critical in detecting if the user is in a good state and not missing functionality, used for system health and used for diagnostic purposes if a user reports an issue with their machine</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="29605-1694">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1694">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1709">**Type** – vrsta trake s obavijesti o licenciranju koja je prikazana korisniku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1709">**Type** – The type of the licensing busbar shown to the user</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="29605-1732">Kada je uređaj na modernom stogu za licenciranje, licencnu datoteku pokušavamo dohvatiti izravno sa servisa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1732">When the device is on the modern licensing stack, we try to get a license file directly from the service.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="29605-1733">Događaj prijavljuje uspjeh ili pogrešku zajedno s eventualnom šifrom pogreške poziva servisu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1733">This event reports the success or failure along with the error code of that service call.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="29605-1734">Ključan je za otkrivanje je li korisnik u dobrom stanju na modernom stogu za licenciranje, koristi se u svrhe određivanja stanja sustava i za dijagnostiku ako korisnik prijavi problem s računalom</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1734">It is critical to detect if the user is in a good state on the modern licensing stack, used for system health and used for diagnostic purposes if a user reports an issue with their machine .</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="29605-1735">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1735">The following fields are collected:</span></span>
