### <a name="officelicensingnulvalidationfullvalidation"></a><span data-ttu-id="29605-1738">Office.Licensing.Nul.Validation.FullValidation</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1738">Office.Licensing.Nul.Validation.FullValidation</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="29605-1739">To se prikuplja tijekom svake sesije uređaja koji koristi moderni stog za licenciranje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1739">This is collected on every session of a device that is running on the modern licensing stack.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="29605-1740">Prijavljuje stanje licence računala i pogreške koje se korisniku prikazuju i zbog kojih ne može koristiti aplikaciju. Događaj naznačuje je li korisnikovo računalo u dobrom stanju na modernom stogu za licenciranje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1740">It reports the licensing state of the machine and reports the errors that the user is seeing due to which they are not able to use the app This event indicates if the user's machine is healthy on the modern licensing stack.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="29605-1741">Za taj smo događaj postavili otkrivanje anomalija da bismo prepoznali uzrokuje li regresija negativno ponašanje korisnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1741">We have anomaly detection set up for this event to indicate if a regression is causing bad user behavior.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="29605-1742">Ključno je i za dijagnosticiranje korisničkih problema te za praćenje stanja sustava.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1742">This is also critical when diagnosing user issues and for monitoring system health.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="29605-1743">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1743">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1744">**Acid** – GUID identifikator koji predstavlja proizvod sustava Office za koji korisnik ima licencu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1744">**Acid** - A GUID identifier representing the Office product that the user is licensed for</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1745">**AllAcids** – popis svih GUID-ova proizvoda za koje je korisnik trenutno licenciran</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1745">**AllAcids** – List of all the GUIDs of the product that the user is currently licensed for</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1746">**Category** – kategorija licence za Office koju korisnik koristi </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1746">**Category** - Category of the Office license that the user is using</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1747">**DaysRemaining** – broj dana do isteka trenutne licence za Office </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1747">**DaysRemaining** – Number of days remaining before the current Office license expires</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1748">**LicenseId** – alfanumerički identifikator licence koja je izdana korisniku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1748">**LicenseId** – An alphanumeric identifier of the license that was issued to the user</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1749">**LicenseType** – vrsta licence za Office koju korisnik koristi </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1749">**LicenseType** - Type of the Office license that the user is using</span></span> 

### <a name="officelicensingofficeclientlicensingdolicensevalidation"></a><span data-ttu-id="29605-1750">Office.Licensing.OfficeClientLicensing.DoLicenseValidation</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1750">Office.Licensing.OfficeClientLicensing.DoLicenseValidation</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="29605-1751">To su metapodaci o licenciranju koji se prilikom svakog pokretanja prikupljaju s uređaja, a prijavljuju ACID licence, status licence, vrstu i druga svojstva licence koja su ključna za prepoznavanje skupa značajki koje su korisniku dostupne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1751">This is licensing metadata that is collected from the device on every boot that reports the license acid, license status, type and other properties of the license that are critical in identifying the features set available to the user.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="29605-1752">Ključni su za prepoznavanje skupa značajki koje su korisniku dostupni te utvrđivanje ne nedostaje li korisniku koja funkcija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1752">This is critical in identifying the feature set available to the user and if any functionality is missing for the user.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="29605-1753">Koriste se i za izračune dnevnog broja aktivnih korisnika / mjesečnog broja aktivnih korisnika te za razna druga izvješća različitih timova u sustavu Office (marketing/DIG/licenciranje) jer sadrže informaciju o vrsti proizvoda koju korisnik upotrebljava, o tome je li u pitanju pretplatnički proizvod te nedostaju li mu ključne funkcije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1753">It is also used for Daily active users/Monthly active user calculations and various other reports by various teams across Office as this tells the type product that the user is using, whether it is a subscription product and whether they are missing any critical functionality.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="29605-1754">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1754">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1755">**FullValidationMode** – način rada koji označava da provodimo potpunu provjeru valjanosti potvrde licence</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1755">**FullValidationMode** – Mode indicating that we are in full validation of license verification</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1756">**IsRFM** – označava je li korisnik u načinu rada smanjene funkcionalnosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1756">**IsRFM** – Indicates whether the user is in reduced functionality mode or not</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1757">**IsSCA** – označava je li pokrenut način rada za aktivaciju na zajedničkom računalu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1757">**IsSCA** – Indicates whether we are running in Shared computer activation mode</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1758">**IsSubscription** – označava koristi li korisnik pretplatničku licencu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1758">**IsSubscription** – Indicates whether the user is using a subscription license or not</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1759">**IsvNext** – označava koristimo li moderni stog za licenciranje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1759">**IsvNext** – Indicates whether we are using the new modern licensing stack or not</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1760">**LicenseCategory** – kategorija licence za Office koju korisnik koristi </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1760">**LicenseCategory** - Category of the Office license that the user is using</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1761">**LicenseStatus** – status licence za Office koju korisnik koristi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1761">**LicenseStatus** – Status of the Office license that the user is using</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1762">**LicenseType** – vrsta licence za Office koju korisnik koristi </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1762">**LicenseType** - Type of the Office license that the user is using</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1763">**LicensingACID** – GUID identifikator koji predstavlja proizvod sustava Office za koji korisnik ima licencu </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1763">**LicensingACID** - A GUID identifier representing the Office product that the user is licensed for</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1764">**OlsLicenseId** – alfanumerički identifikator licence koja je izdana korisniku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1764">**OlsLicenseId** - An alphanumeric identifier of the license that was issued to the user</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1765">**SkuIdIsNull** – označava jesmo li naišli na pogrešku zbog koje ne znamo koji proizvod korisnik upotrebljava</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1765">**SkuIdIsNull** – Indicates whether we encountered an error and don't know the product that the user is running</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1766">**SlapiIsNull** – označava jesmo li naišli na problem prilikom popunjavanja jednog od objekata licenciranja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1766">**SlapiIsNull** – Indicates whether we encountered a problem in populating one of the licensing objects</span></span> 

### <a name="officelicensingonlinerepair"></a><span data-ttu-id="29605-1767">Office.Licensing.OnlineRepair</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1767">Office.Licensing.OnlineRepair</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="29605-1768">Ako zbog nekog razloga ne možemo aktivirati korisnika i moramo mu prikazati dijaloški okvir u kojem se od njega traži da se povežu s internetom i pokušaju s koracima za popravak, aktivira se ovaj događaj.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1768">If we are not able to activate a user for some reason and have to show them a dialog that asks them to go online and try repair steps, this event is fired.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="29605-1769">Ključno je radi otkrivanja je li korisnik u dobrom stanju te da mu ne nedostaje neka funkcija, koristi se u svrhe određivanja stanja sustava i za dijagnostiku ako korisnik prijavi problem s računalom</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1769">It is critical in detecting if the user is in a good state and not missing functionality, used for system health and used for diagnostic purposes if a user reports an issue with their machine</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="29605-1770">Događaj ne prikuplja nijedno polje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1770">This event collects no fields.</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingoobetrybuychoice"></a><span data-ttu-id="29605-1771">Office.Licensing.OOBE.TryBuyChoice</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1771">Office.Licensing.OOBE.TryBuyChoice</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="29605-1772">Korisnici sa unaprijed instaliranim sustavom Office na novim strojevima koji nemaju pravo na sustav Office prikazani su u dijaloškom okviru pomoću kojeg mogu isprobati, kupiti ili unijeti ključ proizvoda da bi se licencirali.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1772">Users with pre-installed Office on new machines who have no Office entitlement are shown a dialog through which they can try, buy or enter a product key to get licensed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="29605-1773">Tim se događajem bilježi akcija korisnika u dijaloškom okviru.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1773">This event captures the user action on the dialog.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="29605-1774">Taj se događaj koristi da bi se pratila korisnička akcija poduzeta u dijaloškom okviru koji se prikazuje korisnicima koji nemaju pravo na sustav Office u kojem je Office unaprijed instaliran na računalu i pomaže pri određivanju je li korisnik licenciran ili nelicenciran po dizajnu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1774">This event is used to track the user action taken on the dialog shown to users with no Office entitlement where Office was pre-installed on the machine and helps determining if the user is licensed or unlicensed by design.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="29605-1775">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1775">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1776">**Buy** – govori je li korisnik kliknuo na gumb Buy ili nije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1776">**Buy** - Tells if the user clicked on the buy button or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1777">**ForceAutoActivate** – kaže bi li se trebala pokrenuti aktivacija u aplikaciji ili ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1777">**ForceAutoActivate** - Tells if in-app activation should be attempted or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1778">**GoBackToSignIn** - kaže je li se korisnik htio ponovno prijaviti (možda s drugim računom)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1778">**GoBackToSignIn** - Tells if the user wanted to sign in again (possibly with another account)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1779">**IsPin** – upućuje na to je li korisnik unio PIN</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1779">**IsPin** - Tells if the user entered a pin</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1780">**ProductKey** - govori je li korisnik pokušao unijeti ključ proizvoda</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1780">**ProductKey** - Tells if the user tried to enter a product key</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1781">**Try** – govori je li korisnik kliknuo na gumb Try ili nije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1781">**Try** - Tells if the user clicked on the try button or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1782">**UserDismissed** – to upućuje na to je li korisnik odbacio dijaloški okvir, a time i način rada u načinu mirovanja ili načinu smanjene funkcionalnosti jer nije odabrao kupovinu sustava Office niti probnu verziju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1782">**UserDismissed** - This tells if the user dismissed the dialog and thus would be in grace or reduced functionality mode because they didn't choose to buy office or get a trial</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingpurchase"></a><span data-ttu-id="29605-1783">Office.Licensing.Purchase</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1783">Office.Licensing.Purchase</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="29605-1784">*[Ovaj je događaj uklonjen iz trenutačnih međuverzija sustava Office, ali se i dalje može pojavljivati u starijim međuverzijama.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1784">*[This event has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="29605-1785">Imamo eksperiment u kojem se korisniku nudi mogućnost da isproba i postavi automatsko plaćanje sustava Office izravno iz aplikacije, a da ni u jednom trenutku ne mora izaći iz aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1785">We have an experiment that gives the user an option to try and setup autopay for Office directly from an app without ever leaving the context of the app.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="29605-1786">Ovo prijavljuje uspjeh ili pogrešku tog eksperimenta, te šifru pogreške. Ključno je u otkrivanju je li korisnik u dobrom stanju, te da mu ne nedostaje neka funkcija, koristi se u svrhe određivanja stanja sustava i za dijagnostiku ako korisnik prijavi problem s računalom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1786">This reports the success or failure of that experiment along with the error code It is critical in detecting if the user is in a good state and not missing functionality, used for system health and used for diagnostic purposes if a user reports an issue with their machine.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="29605-1787">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1787">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1788">**StorePurchaseStatus** – predstavlja šifru pogreške / šifru uspjeha poziva za kupnju obavljenog putem Windows trgovine</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1788">**StorePurchaseStatus** – Represents the error code/success code of the purchase call that was made through windows store</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingsearchforsessiontoken"></a><span data-ttu-id="29605-1789">Office.Licensing.SearchForSessionToken</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1789">Office.Licensing.SearchForSessionToken</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="29605-1790">Ako je korisnik u načinu rada za aktivaciju na zajedničkom računalu, pokušavamo potražiti token sesije na računalu koji korisniku omogućuje upotrebu aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1790">If the user is running under shared computer activation mode, we try to search for a session token on the machine which allows the user to use the app.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="29605-1791">Ovaj događaj prijavljuje uspjeh ili pogrešku tog scenarija, te šifru pogreške. Ključan je za otkrivanje je li korisnik u dobrom stanju, te da mu ne nedostaje neka funkcija, koristi se u svrhe određivanja stanja sustava i za dijagnostiku ako korisnik prijavi problem s računalom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1791">This event reports the success or failure of the scenario along with the error code It is critical in detecting if the user is in a good state and not missing functionality, used for system health and used for diagnostic purposes if a user reports an issue with their machine.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="29605-1792">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1792">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1793">**LoadLicenseResult** – predstavlja šifru pogreške / šifru uspjeha učitavanja licenci za trenutnog korisnika</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1793">**LoadLicenseResult** – Represents the error code/success code of whether we were able to load the licenses for the current user</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1794">**OpportunisticTokenRenewalAttempted** – označava jesmo li oportunistički pokušali obnoviti token za korisnikovu sesiju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1794">**OpportunisticTokenRenewalAttempted** – Indicates whether we attempted to renew the user's session token opportunistically</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1795">**SetAcidResult** – predstavlja šifru pogreške / šifru uspjeha postavljanja ACID-a na očekivanu vrijednost</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1795">**SetAcidResult** – Represent the error code/success code of whether we were able to set the acid to the expected value</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingshownewdeviceactivationdialog"></a><span data-ttu-id="29605-1796">Office.Licensing.ShowNewDeviceActivationDialog</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1796">Office.Licensing.ShowNewDeviceActivationDialog</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="29605-1797">Prilikom prvog pokretanja neke aplikacije sustava Office pokušat ćemo prikazati dijaloški okvir za prijavu koji je unaprijed popunjen vjerodajnicama koje je korisnik upotrijebio za preuzimanje sustava Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1797">On the first boot of an Office app, we will try to show a sign in dialog pre-populated with the credentials the user employed to download Office.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="29605-1798">Korisnik se potom može prijaviti pomoću tih vjerodajnica, unijeti druge vjerodajnice ili odbaciti dijaloški okvir.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1798">The user can then continue to sign-in with those credentials, use different credentials or dismiss the dialog.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="29605-1799">Događaj prijavljuje radnju koju je korisnik poduzeo kad mu se prikazao dijaloški okvir.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1799">This event reports the action taken by the user when presented with this dialog.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="29605-1800">Ključan je za otkrivanje je li korisnik u dobrom stanju na modernom stogu za licenciranje, koristi se u svrhe određivanja stanja sustava i za dijagnostiku ako korisnik prijavi problem s računalom</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1800">It is critical for detecting if a user is in a good state on the modern licensing stack, used for system health and used for diagnostic purposes if a user reports an issue with their machine</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="29605-1801">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1801">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1802">**UserAction** – identifikator radnje koju je korisnik poduzeo kad mu se prikazao dijaloški okvir.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1802">**UserAction** – Identifier for the action taken by the user when presented with the dialog.</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingskutoskuconversion"></a><span data-ttu-id="29605-1803">Office.Licensing.SkuToSkuConversion</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1803">Office.Licensing.SkuToSkuConversion</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="29605-1804">Ako prilikom licenciranja korisnika moramo korisnikov SKU promijeniti iz jednog u drugi, šaljemo ovaj signal zajedno sa šifrom uspjeha ili pogreške.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1804">As part of licensing the user, if we have to change the user's SKU from one SKU to another, we send this signal out along with the success or failure code.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="29605-1805">Ključno je radi otkrivanja je li korisnik u dobrom stanju te da mu ne nedostaje neka funkcija, koristi se u svrhe određivanja stanja sustava i za dijagnostiku ako korisnik prijavi problem s računalom</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1805">It is critical in detecting if the user is in a good state and missing functionality, used for system health and used for diagnostic purposes if a user reports an issue with their machine.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="29605-1806">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1806">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1807">**DestinationSku** – naziv SKU-a u koji je potrebno pretvoriti trenutno instaliran proizvod</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1807">**DestinationSku** – Name of the SKU to which the currently installed product should be converted to</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1808">**PendingAcid** – ID proizvoda za koji je na čekanju pretvorbe SKU-a</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1808">**PendingAcid** – ID of the product for which a SKU conversion is pending</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1809">**SourceSku** – naziv izvornog SKU-a instaliranog na računalu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1809">**SourceSku** – Name of the original SKU that was installed on the machine</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1810">**UninstallProduct** – označava hoće li se stari proizvod deinstalirati prilikom pretvorbe</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1810">**UninstallProduct** – Indicates whether the old product will be uninstalled as part of the conversion</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingtelemetryflowolsresults"></a><span data-ttu-id="29605-1811">Office.Licensing.TelemetryFlow.OLSResults</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1811">Office.Licensing.TelemetryFlow.OLSResults</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="29605-1812">Kada korisnik nema licencirani program, obavit ćemo nekoliko poziva servisa da bismo korisnika doveli u licencirano stanje i aktivirali proizvod sustava Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1812">When a user is unlicensed, we make several service calls to get the user into a licensed state and to activate their Office product.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="29605-1813">Taj se događaj aktivira na poziv servisa za licenciranje sustava Office da bismo provjerili ima li korisnik pravo na njih.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1813">This event gets triggered on calling the Office Licensing Service to check if the user has entitlements.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="29605-1814">Taj će se događaj koristiti za praćenje zdravlja licence korisnika nakon pozivanja servisa za licenciranje sustava Office i zdravlja klijenta sustava Office nakon pokušaja aktivacije sustava Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1814">This event is going to be used to track the user licensing health after calling the Office Licensing Service and the Office Client health after attempting to get Office activated.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="29605-1815">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1815">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1816">**EntitlementPickerShown**- upućuje na to je li korisnik imao više prava, te je li korisnik morao ručno odabrati da bi se licencirao</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1816">**EntitlementPickerShown** - Tells if the user had multiple entitlements and if the user had to manually choose from them to get licensed</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1817">**GetAuthResult** – navodi različita stanja u kojima klijent može biti ako ima prazan ključ proizvoda iz servisa za licenciranje sustava Office ili ako ima pravo na neki drugi proizvod, a Office mora biti pretvoren u novi proizvod</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1817">**GetAuthResult** - Tells various states the client might be in like if they got an empty product key from the Office Licensing Service or if they were entitled for another product and Office needs to be converted to the new product</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1818">**GetEntitlementsCount** – Broj prava koja korisnik ima</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1818">**GetEntitlementsCount** - Tells the number of entitlements the user has</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1819">**GetEntitlementsSucceeded** – upućuje na to je li poziv API-ja za licenciranje sustava Office za dohvaćanje prava korisnika uspio ili nije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1819">**GetEntitlementsSucceeded** - Tells if the call to an Office Licensing Service API to retrieve the user's entitlements succeeded or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1820">**GetKeySucceeded** – upućuje na to je li poziv API-ja za licenciranje sustava Office za dohvaćanje ključa uspio ili nije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1820">**GetKeySucceeded** - Tells if the call to an Office Licensing Service API to retrieve a key succeeded</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1821">**GetNextUserLicenseResult** – kaže može li moderni stog za licenciranje funkcionirati i je li korisnik dobio licencu ili nije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1821">**GetNextUserLicenseResult** - Tells if the modern licensing stack was able to work and if the user got licensed or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1822">**InstallKeyResult** – objašnjava različite razloge zašto je korisnik možda u lošem stanju, primjerice da aktivacija nije uspjela ili nije uspjelo instaliranje ključa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1822">**InstallKeyResult** - Tells various reasons why the user might be in a bad state like if activation failed or the installation of the key failed</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1823">**NotInitializedBeforeWhileAdding** – to je samo informativno i govori da je događaj dodan u mapu telemetrijskog upravitelja bez eksplicitnog registriranja za nju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1823">**NotInitializedBeforeWhileAdding** - This is just informational and tells if the event was added to a telemetry manager map without explicitly registering for it</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1824">**NotInitializedBeforeWhileSending** – to je samo informativno i govori da se događaj pokušao dodati u mapu telemetrijskog upravitelja bez eksplicitnog registriranja unaprijed za nju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1824">**NotInitializedBeforeWhileSending** - This is just informational and tells if the event was attempted to be sent without explicitly registering for it in the telemetry manager map before hand</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1825">**SentOnDestruction** – to je samo informativno i govori da je događaj dodan u mapu telemetrijskog upravitelja bez eksplicitnog slanja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1825">**SentOnDestruction** - This is just informational and tells if the event was added to a telemetry manager map and wasn't sent explicitly</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1826">**Tag** – koristi se za određivanje mjesta u kodu s kojeg je poslan događaj</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1826">**Tag** - Used for telling where in the code the event was sent from</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1827">**VerifyEntitlementsResult** – navodi različita stanja u kojima bi korisnik mogao biti nakon provjere prava dohvaćenih iz servisa za licenciranje sustava Office</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1827">**VerifyEntitlementsResult** - Tells various states the user might be in after validating the entitlements retrieved from the Office Licensing Service</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingtelemetryflowsearchforbindingresult"></a><span data-ttu-id="29605-1828">Office.Licensing.TelemetryFlow.SearchForBindingResult</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1828">Office.Licensing.TelemetryFlow.SearchForBindingResult</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="29605-1829">OEM-ovi prodaju strojeve koji isporučuju sa sustavom Office (jednogodišnja ili neprekidna pretplata).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1829">OEMs sell machines that come with Office (one-year subscriptions or perpetual).</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="29605-1830">Ti se proizvodi sustava Office plaćaju kada kupac kupi uređaj.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1830">These Office products are paid for when the customer purchases their machine.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="29605-1831">Strojevi koje se podešava pomoću određenog regkey-a (OOBEMode: OBIS) možda imaju povezane obveze sustava Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1831">Machines that are setup with a specific regkey (OOBEMode: OEMTA) might have an Office binding associated with it.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="29605-1832">Prilikom dizanja sustava Office na takvim strojevima obavljamo servisne provjere da bismo saznali je li pronađena obveza sustava Office koja odgovara stroju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1832">When we boot Office on such machines, we perform service checks to see if an Office binding corresponding to the machine is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="29605-1833">Ta telemetrijska aktivnost prati točke uspjeha i neuspjeha u traženju povezivanja da bismo mogli osigurati da ih strojevi koji imaju obveze mogu uspješno dohvatiti i da su naši servisi zdravi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1833">This telemetry activity tracks the success and failure points in searching for a binding so that we can ensure that machines that do have a binding can successfully fetch them, and that our services are healthy.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="29605-1834">Ta aktivnost ne prati strojeve bez obveza koji nisu povezani s njima kada provjerimo naše servise.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1834">This activity does not track machines that turn out to not have any bindings associated with them after we check with our services.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="29605-1835">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1835">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1836">**DexShouldRetry** – signal da smo naišli na problem koji se može ponovo pokušati (nema internetskih ni poslužiteljskih kvarova)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1836">**DexShouldRetry** - Signal that we’ve hit a retryable issue (no internet or servers are down)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1837">**GenuineTicketFailure** – govori HRESULT neuspjeha kad pokušavamo dobiti originalnu Windows karticu/ključ proizvoda (WPK).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1837">**GenuineTicketFailure** - Tells us the failure HRESULT when trying to get the machine's Windows genuine ticket/product key (WPK).</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1838">**PinValidationFailure** – govori zašto proces provjere valjanosti PIN-a nije uspio.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1838">**PinValidationFailure** - Tells us why the pin validation process failed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="29605-1839">Moguće pogreške:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1839">Possible errors:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1840">GeoBlocked</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1840">GeoBlocked</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1841">InvalidFormat</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1841">InvalidFormat</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1842">InvalidPin</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1842">InvalidPin</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1843">InvalidState</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1843">InvalidState</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1844">InvalidVersion</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1844">InvalidVersion</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1845">Nepoznato</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1845">Unknown</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1846">Iskorišteno</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1846">Used</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1847">**PinValidationResult** – govori nam rezultat provjere valjanosti PIN-a kojeg nismo uspjeli provaliti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1847">**PinValidationResult** - Tells us the pin validation result of a pin that we failed to crack.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1848">**Pkpn** - pkpn raspon kojem PIN pripada.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1848">**Pkpn** - The pkpn range that the pin belongs to.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1849">**Success** - ukazuje na to da smo uspješno dohvatili valjanu Office obvezu (PIN) za stroj.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1849">**Success** - Indicates that we successfully fetched a valid Office binding (pin) for the machine.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1850">**Tag** – govori nam da smo prestali tražiti obveze.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1850">**Tag** - Tells us at which step we stopped searching for a binding.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="29605-1851">Moguće oznake:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1851">Possible tags:</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1852">0x03113809    Nema Interneta/usluge greška prilikom provjere valjanosti PIN-a</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1852">0x03113809    No internet/service error while validating pin</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1853">0x0311380a    Neuspjela provjera valjanosti PIN-a, poslano s poljem PinValidationFailure</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1853">0x0311380a    Pin validation failure, sent with PinValidationFailure field</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1854">0x0310410f    Uspjeh, poslano s poljem Uspjeh</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1854">0x0310410f    Success, sent with Success field</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1855">0x0311380d    Greške koje je moguće ponovno pokrenuti (problemi s Internetom, nepoznate greške)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1855">0x0311380d    Retry-able errors (internet issues, unknown errors)</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1856">0x0311380e    Greške koje nije moguće ponovno pokrenuti (istekla obvezujuća ponuda)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1856">0x0311380e    Non-retry-able errors (binding offer expired)</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1857">0x0311380f    Ostale greške (licenciranje nije moguće)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1857">0x0311380f    Other errors (unable to license)</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1858">0x03104111    Nije uspjelo provaljivanje PIN-a za Office, poslano s poljem PinValidationResult</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1858">0x03104111    Failed to crack the Office pin, sent with PinValidationResult field</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1859">**WpkBindingFailure** – upućuje nas na kôd pogreške prilikom dobivanja PIN-a za Office vezanog uz WPK za računalo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1859">**WpkBindingFailure** - Tells us the error code of getting the Office pin bound to the machine's WPK.</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingtelemetryflowshowafodialogs"></a><span data-ttu-id="29605-1860">Office.Licensing.TelemetryFlow.ShowAFODialogs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1860">Office.Licensing.TelemetryFlow.ShowAFODialogs</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="29605-1861">Nakon uspješnog dobivanja valjanog PIN-a za Office vezanog uz uređaj koji je unaprijed u paketu sa sustavom Office, korisniku smo prikazali dijaloški okvir za prijavu ili okvir otkupa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1861">After successfully obtaining a valid Office pin bound to a machine pre-bundled with Office, we show the user either a sign-in dialog or a redemption dialog.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="29605-1862">Kada se PIN otkupi, prikazat će se dijaloški okvir EULA.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1862">Once the pin is redeemed, we show the EULA dialog.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="29605-1863">U sklopu naše modernizacijske značajke AFO osvježili smo dva dijaloška okvira da bismo prenijeli dodatne informacije o proizvodu sustava Office koji se isporučuje uz uređaj.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1863">As a part of our modernizing AFO feature, we refreshed the two dialogs to convey more information regarding the Office product that comes with the machine.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="29605-1864">Ta telemetrija prati smanjuje li naša značajka uspješno korisnikovo trenje u otkupljenju proizvoda praćenjem tokova i izlaznih točaka procesa otkupa (za što je dijaloški okvir odbijen).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1864">This telemetry is to track if our feature successfully reduces user friction in redeeming their product by tracking the flow and exit points of the redemption process (which dialog was dismissed).</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="29605-1865">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1865">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1866">**ActionActivate** – signal da je korisnik kliknuo gumb „Aktiviraj”.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1866">**ActionActivate** - Signal that user clicked the “Activate” button.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1867">**ActionChangeAccount** – signal da je korisnik kliknuo hipervezu „Upotrijebi drugi račun”.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1867">**ActionChangeAccount** -  Signal that user clicked the “Use a different account” hyperlink.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1868">**ActionCreateAccount** – signal da je korisnik kliknuo gumb „Stvori račun”.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1868">**ActionCreateAccount** - Signal that user clicked the “Create account” button.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1869">**ActionSignIn** – signal da je korisnik kliknuo gumb „Prijava”.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1869">**ActionSignIn** - Signal that user clicked the “Sign in” button.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1870">**CurrentView** – vrsta dijaloškog okvira koji je korisnik zatvorio.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1870">**CurrentView** - The type of dialog the user closed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1871">**DialogEULA** – signal da smo prikazali dijaloški okvir „Prihvati EULA-u”.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1871">**DialogEULA** -  Signal that we showed the ‘Accept EULA’ dialog.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1872">**DialogRedemption** – signal da smo prikazali dijaloški okvir za iskorištavanje AFO-a.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1872">**DialogRedemption** - Signal that we showed the AFO redemption dialog.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1873">**DialogSignIn** – signal da smo prikazali dijaloški okvir za prijavu u AFO-a.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1873">**DialogSignIn** - Signal that we showed the AFO sign-in dialog.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1874">**EmptyRedemptionDefaults** – signal da nismo uspjeli dohvatiti zadane informacije o iskorištavanju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1874">**EmptyRedemptionDefaults** - Signal that we failed to fetch default redemption information.</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1875">**GetRedemptionInfo** – signal da dohvaćamo demografske podatke ili podatke o iskorištavanju PIN-a.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1875">**GetRedemptionInfo** - Signal that we’re fetching demographic information for pin redemption.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1876">**MalformedCountryCode** – signal da je kôd države koji je potreban za iskorištavanje PIN-a pogrešno oblikovan.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1876">**MalformedCountryCode** - Signal that the country code needed for pin redemption is malformed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1877">**OExDetails** – pojedinosti pogreške koju ćemo vratiti kada je odbijen dijaloški okvir za prijavu identiteta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1877">**OExDetails** - The error details we get back when identity's sign-in dialog was dismissed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1878">**OExType** – vrsta pogreške koju ćemo vratiti kada je odbijen dijaloški okvir za prijavu identiteta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1878">**OExType** - The error type we get back when identity's sign-in dialog was dismissed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1879">**Tag** – govori nam u kojem trenutku korisnik izlazi iz procesa AFO otkupa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1879">**Tag** - Tells us at which step the user exits the AFO redemption process.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="29605-1880">Moguće oznake:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1880">Possible tags:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1881">0x0311380b    Korisnik je odbacio dijaloški okvir za prijavu iz dijaloškog okvira za otkup</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1881">0x0311380b    User dismissed identity's sign-in dialog from redemption dialog</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1882">0x0311380c    Nije uspjelo automatsko učitavanje prijave za prijavu identiteta korisnika iz dijaloškog okvira za otkup</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1882">0x0311380c    Failed to auto-load an identity post user sign-in from redemption dialog</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1883">0x03113810    Nije uspjelo učitavanje demografskih informacija o računu (pozivni broj za državu, jezične, valutne i marketinške preferencije te probna ponuda)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1883">0x03113810    Failed to load the account's demographic information (country code, language,     currency, trial offer, and marketing preferences)</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1884">0x03113805    Korisnik je odbacio dijaloški okvir za prijavu identiteta iz dijaloškog okvira za prijavu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1884">0x03113805    User dismissed identity's sign-in dialog from sign-in dialog</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1885">0x03113806    Nije uspjelo automatsko učitavanje prijave identiteta korisnika iz dijaloškog okvira za prijavu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1885">0x03113806    Failed to auto-load an identity post user sign-in from sign-in dialog</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1886">0x03113807 Nije uspjelo automatsko učitavanje identiteta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1886">0x03113807    Failed to auto-load an identity</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1887">0x03113811 Korisnik je završio dijaloški okvir za prijavu/otkup</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1887">0x03113811    User closed the sign-in/redemption dialog</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1888">0x03113812 Korisnik je završio dijaloški okvir Prihvati EULA</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1888">0x03113812    User closed the accept EULA dialog</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1889">0x03113808 Korisnik je prihvatio EULA</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1889">0x03113808    User accepted the EULA</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1890">0x03113811 Korisnik je zatvorio dijaloški okvir</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1890">0x03113811      User closed a dialog</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1891">0x2370e3a0 Korisnik je zatvorio dijaloški okvir</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1891">0x2370e3a0      User closed a dialog</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1892">0x2370e3c1 Idite na web-mjesto za iskorištavanje PIN-a</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1892">0x2370e3c1      Go to web for pin redemption</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1893">0x2370e3a1 Idite na web-mjesto za iskorištavanje PIN-a</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1893">0x2370e3a1      Go to web for pin redemption</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1894">0x2370e3c0 Petlja dijaloških sekvenci koja je uzrokovana korisnikovim pomicanjem unatrag i unaprijed u dijaloškom toku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1894">0x2370e3c0      Dialog sequence looped caused by user going back and forth in the dialog flow</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1895">0x2370e3a3 Korisnik je kliknuo vezu „Ne sada” kojom se preskače ponuda AFO-a za tu sesiju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1895">0x2370e3a3      User clicked “Not now” hyperlink which skips the AFO offer for that session</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1896">0x2370e3a2 Korisnik je kliknuo hipervezu „Nikad mi to ne prikazuj” kojom se onemogućuje ponuda AFO-a</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1896">0x2370e3a2      User clicked on “Never show this to me” hyperlink which disables the AFO offer</span></span>


- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1897">**UseInAppRedemption** – govori nam držimo li korisnike u aplikaciji za otkup ili ih šaljemo na web da bi iskoristili svoj dohvaćeni PIN (unaprijed popunjeni).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1897">**UseInAppRedemption** - Tells us if we're keeping users in-app for redemption or sending them to the web to redeem their fetched pin (pre-populated).</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1898">**UseModernAFO** – govori nam koristimo li novo ili staro iskustvo za AFO.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1898">**UseModernAFO** - Tells us if we're using the new or old AFO experience.</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingtelemetryflowshowtrybuydialogforoobe"></a><span data-ttu-id="29605-1899">Office.Licensing.TelemetryFlow.ShowTryBuyDialogForOOBE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1899">Office.Licensing.TelemetryFlow.ShowTryBuyDialogForOOBE</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="29605-1900">Kada novi aparati imaju unaprijed instaliranu verziju sustava Office, a korisnik nema pravo, prikazat će se dijaloški okvir koji korisniku omogućuje da proba, kupi ili unese ključ proizvoda kako bi se licencirao i taj događaj prati je li prikazan dijaloški okvir.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1900">When new machines have Office pre-installed and the user doesn't have an entitlement we show a dialog which gives the user the option to try, buy or enter a product key so that the user can get licensed and this event tracks if the dialog was shown.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="29605-1901">Taj će vam događaj pomoći da saznate je li korisniku prikazao dijaloški okvir za isprobavanje, kupnju ili unos ključa za proizvoda, a time ćete nam pomoći da utvrdimo je li korisnik imao mogućnost kupnje licenciranog sustava.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1901">This event will help with knowing if the dialog was shown to the user to try, buy or enter the product key and hence will help us determine if the user had the opportunity to get licensed.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="29605-1902">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1902">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1903">**ActiveView** – daje ID dijaloškog okvira koji se prikazuje korisniku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1903">**ActiveView** - Tells the dialog ID shown to the user</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1904">**CurrentOOBEMode**- govori koji je način rada za pred-instaliranje (način rada OOBE, npr. AFO, OEM itd.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1904">**CurrentOOBEMode** - Tells the pre-install mode (OOBE mode such as AFO, OEM etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1905">**NotInitializedBeforeWhileAdding** – to je samo informativno i govori da je događaj dodan u mapu telemetrijskog upravitelja bez eksplicitnog registriranja za nju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1905">**NotInitializedBeforeWhileAdding** - This is just informational and tells if the event was added to a telemetry manager map without explicitly registering for it</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1906">**SentOnDestruction** – to je samo informativno i govori da je događaj dodan u mapu telemetrijskog upravitelja bez eksplicitnog slanja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1906">**SentOnDestruction** - This is just informational and tells if the event was added to a telemetry manager map and wasn't sent explicitly</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1907">**ShowTryButton** – govori je li gumb Try prikazan korisniku u dijaloškom okviru ili nije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1907">**ShowTryButton** - Tells if the Try Button was shown to the user on the dialog or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1908">**Tag** – koristi se za određivanje mjesta u kodu s kojeg je poslan događaj</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1908">**Tag** - Used for telling where in the code the event was sent from</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingtelemetryflowtrialflow"></a><span data-ttu-id="29605-1909">Office.Licensing.TelemetryFlow.TrialFlow</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1909">Office.Licensing.TelemetryFlow.TrialFlow</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="29605-1910">Kada nelicencirani korisnik sustava Office koji je unaprijed instaliran na stroju proba doći do probne verzije, taj će se događaj aktivirati.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1910">When an unlicensed user of Office pre-installed on a machine is attempting to get a trial, this event gets triggered.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="29605-1911">Koristi se da bi se prikazala putanja koju korisnik slijediti da bi dobio probnu verziju i ako je došlo do grešaka prilikom dobivanja probne verzije putem kupnje u aplikaciji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1911">It is used to see which path the user would follow to get a trial and if there were any errors while getting the trial through in-app purchases.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="29605-1912">Ovisno o korisnikovoj akciji i rezultatu kupnje u aplikaciji, korisnik može završiti kao da nije licenciran.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1912">Depending on the user action and the result of the in-app purchase the user could end up being unlicensed.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="29605-1913">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1913">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1914">**HasConnectivity** – govori ima li korisnik internetsku vezu, a u slučaju da ona ne postoji, korisnik možda koristi licencu za poček za pet dana ili je možda u načinu rada s smanjenom funkcionalnošću</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1914">**HasConnectivity** - Tells if the user has internet connectivity and in case there isn't the user might have to use a grace license for five days or may be in reduced functionality mode</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1915">**InAppTrialPurchase** – upućuje na to je li za pokretanje SDK za kupnju u trgovini omogućeno snimanje PI-a i kupnja iz probne aplikacije *[Ovo je polje uklonjeno iz trenutačnih međuverzija sustava Office, ali se i dalje može pojavljivati u starijim međuverzijama.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1915">**InAppTrialPurchase** - Tells if the flight is enabled for launching the Store Purchase SDK to capture PI and purchase a trial from within the application *[This field has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1916">**IsRS1OrGreater** – upućuje na to je li verzija sustava veća od RS1 ili ne, jer se SDK za kupnju u trgovini može koristiti samo ako je verzija OS-a veća od RS1</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1916">**IsRS1OrGreater** - Tells if the OS Version is greater than RS1 or not since the Store Purchase SDK should be used only if the OS Version is greater that RS1</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1917">**NotInitializedBeforeWhileAdding** – to je samo informativno i govori da je događaj dodan u mapu telemetrijskog upravitelja bez eksplicitnog registriranja za nju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1917">**NotInitializedBeforeWhileAdding**: This is just informational and tells if the event was added to a telemetry manager map without explicitly registering for it</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1918">**OEMSendToWebForTrial** – upućuje na to je li omogućen let za slanje korisnika na web radi iskorištavanja probne verzije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1918">**OEMSendToWebForTrial** - Tells if the flight is enabled to send users to the web to redeem a trial</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1919">**StoreErrorConditions** – upućuje na različite uvjete u kojima je SDK za kupnju u trgovini možda neuspio *[Ovo je polje uklonjeno iz trenutačnih međuverzija sustava Office, ali se i dalje može pojavljivati u starijim međuverzijama.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1919">**StoreErrorConditions** - Tells the various conditions under which the Store Purchase SDK could have failed *[This field has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1920">**StoreErrorHResult** – upućuje na kôd pogreške vraćen iz SDK za kupnju u trgovini *[Ovo je polje uklonjeno iz trenutačnih međuverzija sustava Office, ali se i dalje može pojavljivati u starijim međuverzijama.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1920">**StoreErrorHResult** - Tells the error code returned from the Store Purchase SDK *[This field has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1921">**StorePurchaseStatusResult** – daje rezultat poziva SDK za kupnju u trgovini i je li korisnik obavio kupnju ili nije, što će pomoći odrediti hoće li korisnik imati licencu za korištenje sustava Office *[Ovo je polje uklonjeno iz trenutačnih međuverzija sustava Office, ali se i dalje može pojavljivati u starijim međuverzijama.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1921">**StorePurchaseStatusResult** - Tells the result of calling the Store Purchase SDK and if the user made a purchase or not which will help determine if the user should get licensed to use Office *[This field has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1922">**Tag** – upotrebljava se za određivanje mjesta u kodu s kojeg je poslan događaj</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1922">**Tag** - Used for telling where in the code the event was sent from</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1923">**UserSignedInExplicitly** – govori je li se korisnik potpisao eksplicitno jer ćemo u tomu slučaju ponovno usmjeriti korisnike na web-mjesto za probnu verziju *[Ovo je polje uklonjeno iz trenutačnih međuverzija sustava Office, ali se i dalje može pojavljivati u starijim međuverzijama.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1923">**UserSignedInExplicitly** - Tells if the user signed in explicitly in which case, we would re-direct users to the web for the trial *[This field has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

### <a name="officelicensingusegracekey"></a><span data-ttu-id="29605-1924">Office.Licensing.UseGraceKey</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1924">Office.Licensing.UseGraceKey</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="29605-1925">Ako zbog nekog razloga ne možemo licencirati korisnika, instaliramo privremeni ključ i šaljemo signal koji to označava.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1925">For some reason if we are unable to license the user, we install a grace key and send out this signal that signifies.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="29605-1926">Ključno je radi otkrivanja je li korisnik u dobrom stanju te da mu ne nedostaje neka funkcija, koristi se u svrhe određivanja stanja sustava i za dijagnostiku ako korisnik prijavi problem s računalom</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1926">It is critical in detecting if the user is in a good state and missing functionality, used for system health and used for diagnostic purposes if a user reports an issue with their machine</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="29605-1927">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1927">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1928">**OpportunisticTokenRenewalAttempted** – označava jesmo li pokušali oportunistički obnoviti korisnika u načinu rada za licenciranje zajedničkog računala</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1928">**OpportunisticTokenRenewalAttempted** – Indicates if we attempted an opportunistic renewal for the user in shared computer activation mode</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1929">**ReArmResult** – označava rezultat ponovne aktivacije instalacijskog ključa koji može produljiti vrijeme do isteka trenutne licence</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1929">**ReArmResult** – Indicates the result of rearming the installed key which can extend the expiry of the current license</span></span>

### <a name="onenoteenrollmentresult"></a><span data-ttu-id="29605-1930">OneNote.EnrollmentResult</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1930">OneNote.EnrollmentResult</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="29605-1931">Tim se događajem zapisuje status prilikom uključivanja u Intune.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1931">This event logs the status upon Intune enrollment.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="29605-1932">Taj je scenarij specifičan za korištenje računa omogućenih za Intune.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1932">This scenario is specific to Intune enabled accounts.</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="29605-1933">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1933">The following fields are collected:</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1934">**EnrollmentResult**- rezultat upisa u Intune</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1934">**EnrollmentResult** - The result of Intune enrollment</span></span>

## <a name="microsoft-autoupdate-mau-events"></a><span data-ttu-id="29605-1935">Događaji Microsoftova automatskog ažuriranja (MAU)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1935">Microsoft AutoUpdate (MAU) events</span></span>

### <a name="appdelegate_launch"></a><span data-ttu-id="29605-1936">appdelegate_launch</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1936">appdelegate_launch</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="29605-1937">Taj događaj označava da je došlo do pokušaja pokretanja aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1937">This event denotes that an attempt to launch the app occurred.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="29605-1938">Evidentiramo rezultat (neuspjeh ili uspjeh).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1938">We log its result (failure or success).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="29605-1939">Koristimo ovaj događaj da identificiramo slučajeve u kojima se MAU ne uspije pokrenuti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1939">We use this event to identify cases in which MAU fails to launch</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="29605-1940">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1940">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1941">**App** – Proces aplikacije za slanje događaja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1941">**App** - The application process sending the event</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1942">**AppInfo_Language** – Jezik pod kojim se aplikacija izvodi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1942">**AppInfo_Language** - The language the application is running under</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1943">**AppversionLong** – Verzija aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1943">**AppversionLong** - The application version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1944">**Channel** – Preference za publiku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1944">**Channel** - The preference for audience</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1945">**Device_NetworkCountry** – Zemlja uređaja (na temelju IP adrese)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1945">**Device_NetworkCountry** - The device country (based on IP address)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1946">**DeviceID** – Identifikator uređaja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1946">**DeviceID** - The device identifier</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1947">**DeviceInfo_Model** – Hardverski model uređaja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1947">**DeviceInfo_Model** - The Hardware Model of the device</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1948">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** – Vrsta mreže (Wi-Fi, ožičena, nepoznata)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1948">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** - The type of network (Wi-Fi, Wired, Unknown)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1949">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** – Verzija operacijskog sustava</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1949">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** - The version of the Operating System</span></span>

 - <span data-ttu-id="29605-1950">**Event_ReceivedTime** – Vrijeme primanja telemetrije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1950">**Event_ReceivedTime** - The time at which telemetry was received</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1951">**EventInfo_Name** – Naziv telemetrijskog događaja koji se zapisuje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1951">**EventInfo_Name** - The name of the telemetry event being logged</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1952">**EventInfo_Time** – Vrijeme odvijanja zapisanog događaja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1952">**EventInfo_Time** - The time at which the logged event took place</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1953">**HowTocheck** – Postavka za provjeru ažuriranja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1953">**HowTocheck** - The preference for checking of updates</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1954">**Payload** – Skup statičnog teksta koji pokazuje stanje pokretanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1954">**Payload** - A set of static text indicating launch status.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1955">**PipelineInfo_ClientCountry** – Zemlja uređaja (na temelju IP adrese)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1955">**PipelineInfo_ClientCountry** - The device country (based on IP address)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1956">**PipelineInfo_ClientIp** – Prva 3 okteta IP adrese</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1956">**PipelineInfo_ClientIp** - The first 3 octets of the IP address</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1957">**SessionId** – Identifikator sesije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1957">**SessionId** - The identifier for the session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1970">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** – Verzija operacijskog sustava</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1970">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** - The version of the Operating System</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-1971">**Event_ReceivedTime** – Vrijeme primanja telemetrije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-1971">**Event_ReceivedTime** - The time at which telemetry was received</span></span>

## <a name="onenote-sync-events"></a><span data-ttu-id="29605-5543">Sinkronizacija događaja u programu OneNote</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5543">OneNote sync events</span></span>

### <a name="officeonenotestoragenotebooksyncresult"></a><span data-ttu-id="29605-5544">Office.OneNote.Storage.NotebookSyncResult</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5544">Office.OneNote.Storage.NotebookSyncResult</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="29605-5545">Ovaj događaj zapisuje rezultat sinkronizacije bilježnice.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5545">This event logs notebook sync result.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="29605-5546">Koristi se za otkrivanje broja jedinstvenih ciljeva sinkronizacije tijekom izračuna rezultata sinkronizacije aplikacije OneNote.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5546">It is used for figuring out how many unique sync targets when calculating OneNote sync score.</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="29605-5547">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5547">The following fields are collected</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-5548">**CachedError_Code** – numerirani ili alfanumerički kod koji se koristi za određivanje prirode predmemorirane pogreške i/ili razloga pojave</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5548">**CachedError_Code** - a numbered or alphanumeric code used to determine the nature of the cached error, and/or why it occurred</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-5549">**CachedError_Description** – opis predmemorirane pogreške</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5549">**CachedError_Description** – a description of the cached error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-5550">**CachedError_Tag** – označava mjesto na kojem se predmemorirana pogreška prikazuje u kodu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5550">**CachedError_Tag** – indicate where in the code throws the cached error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-5551">**CachedError_Type** – vrsta predmemorirane pogreške, npr. Win32Error itd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5551">**CachedError_Type** – the type of the cached error, e.g. Win32Error, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-5552">**ExecutionTime** – vrijeme u milisekundama potrebno za repliciranje bilježnice</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5552">**ExecutionTime** – time in milliseconds taken to replicate the notebook</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-5553">**Gosid** – globalni ID prostora objekta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5553">**Gosid** – global object space ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-5554">**IdentityType** – vrsta identiteta, npr. Windows Live, Org ID itd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5554">**IdentityType** – identity type, e.g. Windows Live, Org ID, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-5555">**InitialReplicationInSession** – označava je li ova replikacija prva replikacija bilježnice nakon otvaranja ili nije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5555">**InitialReplicationInSession** – is this replication the first notebook replication after open or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-5556">**IsBackgroundSync** – označava je li ovo sinkronizacija u pozadini ili nije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5556">**IsBackgroundSync** – is this a background sync or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-5557">**IsCachedErrorSuppressed** – označava je li predmemorirana pogreška potisnuta ili nije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5557">**IsCachedErrorSuppressed** – is the cached error suppressed or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-5558">**IsCachedErrorUnexpected** – označava je li predmemorirana pogreška neočekivana ili nije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5558">**IsCachedErrorUnexpected** – is the cached error unexpected or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-5559">**IsNotebookErrorSuppressed** – označava je li pogreška sinkronizacije na razini bilježnice potisnuta ili nije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5559">**IsNotebookErrorSuppressed** – is the notebook level sync error suppressed or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-5560">**IsNotebookErrorUnexpected** – označava je li pogreška sinkronizacije na razini bilježnice neočekivana ili nije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5560">**IsNotebookErrorUnexpected** – is the notebook level sync error unexpected or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-5561">**IsSectionErrorSuppressed** – označava je li pogreška sinkronizacije odjeljka potisnuta ili nije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5561">**IsSectionErrorSuppressed** – is the section sync error suppressed or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-5562">**IsSectionErrorUnexpected** – označava je li pogreška sinkronizacije odjeljka neočekivana ili nije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5562">**IsSectionErrorUnexpected** – is the section sync error unexpected or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-5563">**IsUsingRealtimeSync** – označava koristi li sinkronizacija bilježnice suvremenu sinkronizaciju sadržaja stranice ili ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5563">**IsUsingRealtimeSync** – is the notebook sync using modern page content sync or not</span></span>
