### <a name="officeonenotestoragerealtimewebsocketsessioninfo"></a><span data-ttu-id="29605-5585">Office.OneNote.Storage.RealTime.WebSocketSessionInfo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5585">Office.OneNote.Storage.RealTime.WebSocketSessionInfo</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="29605-5586">Ovaj događaj evidentira rezultat sinkronizacije web-utičnice za obje sinkronizacije aplikacije OneNote: suvremenu sinkronizaciju sadržaja stranice i suvremenu sinkronizaciju hijerarhije. Koristi se za otkrivanje broja jedinstvenih ciljeva sinkronizacije tijekom izračuna rezultata sinkronizacije aplikacije OneNote.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5586">This event logs WebSocket sync result for both OneNote modern page content sync modern hierarchy sync. It is used for figuring out how many unique sync targets when calculating OneNote sync score.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="29605-5587">Također se koristi za suvremenu sinkronizaciju performansi nadzorne ploče u aplikaciji OneNote.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5587">It is also used for OneNote modern sync performance dashboard.</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="29605-5588">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5588">The following fields are collected:</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="29605-5589">**CloseReason** – Razlog zatvaranja web-utičnice, npr. neuobičajeno zatvaranje, itd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5589">**CloseReason** - WebSocket close reason, e.g. Abnormal close, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-5590">**DataIsFreshCount** – broj uspješnih zahtjeva za reviziju koda u sesiji web-utičnice</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5590">**DataIsFreshCount** - number of successful pull requests in the WebSocket session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-5591">**DeviceSessionId** – ID sesije uređaja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5591">**DeviceSessionId** - Device session ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-5592">**DownloadCount** – broj preuzimanja u sesiji web-utičnice</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5592">**DownloadCount** - number of downloads in the WebSocket session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-5593">**Error** – u osnovi je Exception_Type + Exception_Description + Exception_Code + Exception_Tag</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5593">**Error** - is basically Exception_Type + Exception_Description + Exception_Code + Exception_Tag</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-5594">**Exception_Code** – numerirani ili alfanumerički kod koji se koristi za određivanje prirode pogreške i/ili razloga pojave</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5594">**Exception_Code** - a numbered or alphanumeric code used to determine the nature of an error, and/or why it occurred</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-5595">**Exception_Description** – opis pogreške</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5595">**Exception_Description** - a description of the error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-5596">**Exception_Tag** – označava mjesto na kojem se pogreška prikazuje u kodu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5596">**Exception_Tag** - indicate where in the code throws the error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-5597">**Exception_Type** – vrsta pogreške, npr. Win32Error itd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5597">**Exception_Type** - the type of the error, e.g. Win32Error, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-5598">**FirstUpdateSize** – prva duljina ažuriranja poruke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5598">**FirstUpdateSize** - first update message length</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-5599">**HasError** – postoji li pogreška tijekom sesije web-utičnice</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5599">**HasError** - whether there is an error during the WebSocket session</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-5600">**IsEducationNotebook** – označava je li trenutna bilježnica obrazovna bilježnica ili nije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5600">**IsEducationNotebook** - Is the current notebook education notebook or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-5601">**IsHierarchyResource** – označava je li trenutni resurs stranica ili odjeljak</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5601">**IsHierarchyResource** - Is the current resource a page or a section</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-5602">**Notebookid** – ID bilježnice programa OneNote</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5602">**NotebookId** - OneNote notebook ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-5603">**OperationWithError** – u kojoj se operaciji dogodila pogreška, npr. WebSocket.Close, WebSocket.Open, itd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5603">**OperationWithError** - in which operation did the error happen, e.g. WebSocket.Close, WebSocket.Open, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-5604">**ResourceId** – ID resursa stranice ili odjeljka aplikacije OneNote</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5604">**ResourceId** - OneNote page or section resource ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-5605">**SectionId** – ID odjeljka aplikacije OneNote</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5605">**SectionId** - OneNote section ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-5606">**ServerSessionId** – ID sesije koji se koristi za povezivanje zahtjeva web-utičnice s web-mjestom onenote.com</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5606">**ServerSessionId** - session ID used to correlate WebSocket request to onenote.com</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-5607">**SessionDurationInMs** – trajanje sesije web-utičnice u milisekundama</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5607">**SessionDurationInMs** - the duration in milliseconds of the WebSocket session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-5608">**TenantId** – ID klijenta sustava SharePoint</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5608">**TenantId** - SharePoint tenant ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-5609">**TimeToFirstUpdateInMs** – vrijeme u milisekundama potrebno za primanje prvog ažuriranja sa strane poslužitelja nakon uspostavljanja sesije web-utičnice</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5609">**TimeToFirstUpdateInMs** - time in milliseconds taken to receive first update from the server side after the WebSocket session is established</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-5610">**UploadAckCount** – broj potvrda za prijenos u sesiji web-utičnice</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5610">**UploadAckCount** - number of acknowledges for upload in the WebSocket session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-5611">**WebUrl** – PII čišćenje web URL-a</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5611">**WebUrl** - PII scrubbed web URL</span></span>

### <a name="officeonenotestoragesyncscore"></a><span data-ttu-id="29605-5644">Office.OneNote.Storage.SyncScore</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5644">Office.OneNote.Storage.SyncScore</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="29605-5645">Ovaj događaj evidentira sve negativne čimbenike u iskustvu sinkronizacije koji su vidljivi korisnicima.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5645">This event logs all negative factors in sync experience that are visible to users.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="29605-5646">Koristi se za izračunavanje rezultata sinkronizacije programa OneNote, što je kritična metrika za procjenu iskustva sinkronizacije korisnika programa OneNote.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5646">It is used to calculate OneNote sync score, which is a critical metric to evaluate OneNote users' sync experience.</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="29605-5647">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5647">The following fields are collected</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-5648">**AutoShowSyncStatus** – označava je li status sinkronizacije automatski prikazan ili nije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5648">**AutoShowSyncStatus** - whether sync status is auto shown or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-5664">**Source** – identifikator označava koji je događaj pokrenuo korisničko sučelje, tj. stvorio novu Redx sliku, pogrešku sinkronizacije u sučelju za sinkronizaciju, prikazan dijalog pogreške itd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5664">**Source** - an enum indicates which event triggered the UI, i.e. created a new redx image, sync error in the sync UI, error dialog displayed, etc.</span></span>

 - <span data-ttu-id="29605-5690">**Data_EventId** – Kôd koji pokazuje preferenciju prikupljanja podataka koju je odabrao korisnik.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5690">**Data_EventId** – A code indicating the diagnostic data collection preference selected by the user.</span></span>

### <a name="officesystemgracefulexitgracefulappexitdesktop"></a><span data-ttu-id="29605-5691">Office.System.GracefulExit.GracefulAppExitDesktop</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5691">Office.System.GracefulExit.GracefulAppExitDesktop</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="29605-5692">Događaj je aktiviralo skladno ukidanje aplikacije za klijentske aplikacije sustava Office, kao što su, no ne ograničavajući se na Word, Excel, PowerPoint i Outlook.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5692">The event is triggered by a graceful application termination for Office client applications such as, but not limited to, Word, Excel, PowerPoint, and Outlook.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="29605-5693">Parametre skladnog zatvaranja upotrebljavamo za mjerenje stanja proizvoda klijenata sustava Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5693">We use Graceful Exit to measure the health of Office client products.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="29605-5694">To je zamišljeno da bude signal ključan za poslovanje koji inženjeri sustava Office koriste za postizanje stabilnosti proizvoda.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5694">It is intended to be a business-critical signal used by Office engineers to infer product stability.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="29605-5695">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5695">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="29605-5696">**AppBuild** – identifikator međuverzije zahvaćenog procesa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5696">**AppBuild** - Build version identifier for the affected process.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="29605-5697">**AppMajor** – identifikator glavne verzije zahvaćenog procesa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5697">**AppMajor** - Major version identifier for the affected process.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="29605-5698">**AppMinor** – identifikator sporedne verzije zahvaćenog procesa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5698">**AppMinor** - Minor version identifier for the affected process.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="29605-5699">**AppRevision** – identifikator međuverzije zahvaćenog procesa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5699">**AppRevision** - Build version identifier for the affected process.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="29605-5700">**Boot Completed** – dovršio je postupak pokretanja sustava Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5700">**BootCompleted** – Did Office process complete boot.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="29605-5701">**DetectionTime** – vrijeme otkrivanja neočekivanog zatvaranja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5701">**DetectionTime** - The time when the unexpected exit was detected.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="29605-5702">**EcsETag** – identifikator eksperimenta za postupak.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5702">**EcsETag** - An experiment identifier for the process.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="29605-5703">**HasEdit** – uređivanje dokumenta koje se pojavljuje tijekom postupka sustava Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5703">**HasEdit** – Was document editing occurring during the Office process.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="29605-5704">**HasOpen** – dokument je bio otvoren tijekom postupka sustava Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5704">**HasOpen** – Was document opened during the Office process.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="29605-5705">**InstallMethod** – određuje je li sustav nadograđen na trenutačnu međuverziju sustava Office, vraćen na nju ili je u pitanju nova instalacija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5705">**InstallMethod** - Whether the current build of Office was upgraded from, rolled back to, or a fresh install.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="29605-5706">**OfficeUILang** – jezik postupka sustava Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5706">**OfficeUILang** – Language of the Office process.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="29605-5707">**PreviousBuild** – prethodno instalirana međuverzija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5707">**PreviousBuild** - Previously installed build version.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="29605-5708">**SafeMode** – jest postupak sustava Office u sigurnom načinu rada.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5708">**SafeMode** – Was Office process in safe mode.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="29605-5709">**SessionId** – jedinstveni identifikator procesa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5709">**SessionId** - A unique identifier of the process.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="29605-5710">**SessionInitTime** – Vrijeme pokretanja zahvaćenog procesa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-5710">**SessionInitTime** - The time when the affected process started.</span></span>

### <a name="officesystemsystemhealthungracefulapplicationexitwin32"></a><span data-ttu-id="29605-6158">Office.System.SystemHealthUngracefulApplicationExitWin32</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-6158">Office.System.SystemHealthUngracefulApplicationExitWin32</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="29605-6159">Događaj aktivira nenormalno ukidanje aplikacije (npr. zaustavljanje u upravitelju zadataka, prekid aplikacije, itd.) za klijentske aplikacije sustava Office, kao što su, no ne ograničavajući se na, Word, Excel, PowerPoint i Outlook.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-6159">The event is triggers by an abnormal application termination (for example, task manager kill, application hang, etc.) for Office client applications such as, but not limited to, Word, Excel, PowerPoint, and Outlook.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="29605-6160">Parametre neočekivanog zatvaranja aplikacije koristimo za mjerenje stanja proizvoda klijenata sustava Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-6160">We use Ungraceful Application Exit metrics to measure the health of Office client products.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="29605-6161">To je signal ključan za poslovanje koji inženjeri sustava Office koriste za postizanje stabilnosti proizvoda.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-6161">It is a business-critical signal used by Office engineers to infer product stability.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="29605-6162">Prikupljaju se sljedeća polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-6162">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-6163">**AddinExecution –** Zastavica koja obavještava je li izvršavanje dodatka prekinuto prilikom neočekivanog izlaska iz aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-6163">**AddinExecution -** Flag that informs if an add-in was executing and didn't finish during an ungraceful application exit.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-6164">**BootCompleted –** je li dovršeno pokretanje sustava Office u trenutku rušenja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-6164">**BootCompleted –** Was Office boot completed at the time of crash.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-6165">**CrashedAppBuild –** identifikator međuverzije zahvaćenog procesa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-6165">**CrashedAppBuild -** Build version identifier for the affected process.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-6166">**CrashedAppMajor –** identifikator glavne verzije zahvaćenog procesa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-6166">**CrashedAppMajor -** Major version identifier for the affected process.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-6167">**CrashedAppMinor –** identifikator sporedne verzije zahvaćenog procesa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-6167">**CrashedAppMinor -** Minor version identifier for the affected process.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-6168">**CrashedAppRevision –** identifikator međuverzije zahvaćenog procesa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-6168">**CrashedAppRevision -** Build version identifier for the affected process.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-6169">**CrashedEcsETag –** identifikator eksperimenta za srušeni proces.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-6169">**CrashedEcsETag -** An experiment identifier for the crashed process.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-6170">**CrashedModuleName –** naziv neispravnog modula.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-6170">**CrashedModuleName -** Failing module name.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-6171">**CrashedSessionId –** jedinstveni identifikator srušenog procesa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-6171">**CrashedSessionId -** A unique identifier of the crashed process.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-6172">**CrashedSessionInitTime –** vrijeme pokretanja zahvaćenog procesa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-6172">**CrashedSessionInitTime -** The time when the affected process started.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-6173">**CrashTime –** vrijeme koje ukazuje da je klijent neočekivano prekinut.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-6173">**CrashTime –** The time indicating the client terminated ungracefully.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-6174">**CrashType –** identifikator grupiranja za vrstu rušenja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-6174">**CrashType -** Bucketing identifier for the type of crash.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-6175">**DetectionTime –** vrijeme otkrivanja neočekivanog zatvaranja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-6175">**DetectionTime -** The time when the unexpected exit was detected.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-6176">**ExceptionAddress –** adresa u programu na kojoj je došlo do pogreške.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-6176">**ExceptionAddress -** Address in the program where the failure occurred.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-6177">**ExceptionCode –** identifikator grupiranja za iznimku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-6177">**ExceptionCode -** Bucketing identifier for the exception.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-6178">**HandOff –** je li korisnik stvorio i predao Officeov postupak novoj sesiji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-6178">**HandOff –** Did the user create and hand off the Office process to a new session.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-6179">**HasEdit –** je li korisnik uređivao dokument u srušenom klijentu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-6179">**HasEdit –** Was the user editing a document in the crashed client.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-6180">**HasOpen –** je li dokument bio otvoren u srušenom klijentu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-6180">**HasOpen –** Was a document open in the crashed client.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-6181">**HexCrashTag –**  Jedinstveni identifikator kôda rušenja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-6181">**HexCrashTag -**  The unique identifier for the code of the crash.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-6182">**HexExceptionAddress –** heksadecimalni oblik adrese u programu na kojoj je došlo do pogreške.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-6182">**HexExceptionAddress -** Address in hexadecimal in the program where the failure occurred.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-6183">**HexExceptionCode –** heksadecimalni identifikator grupiranja za iznimku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-6183">**HexExceptionCode -** Bucketing identifier in hexadecimal for the exception.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-6184">**HexModuleBaseAddress –** osnovna adresa neispravnog modula u heksadecimalnom obliku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-6184">**HexModuleBaseAddress -** Base Address in hexadecimal of the failing module.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="29605-6185">**HexModuleBaseAddress –** pomak u bajtovima (u heksadecimalnom obliku) od osnovne adrese na kojoj je došlo do pogreške.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="29605-6185">**HexModuleOffset -** Offset in bytes (in hexadecimal) from the base address where the failure occurred.</span></span>
